      <title>美国驳斥纽约市长声称指控不构成犯罪的说法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/us-defends-bribery-charge-nyc-mayor-claims-is-no-crime-at-all</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官反驳了纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯的说法，即他们上个月对他提起的贿赂指控“根本不构成联邦罪行”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/us-defends-bribery-charge-nyc-mayor-claims-is-no-crime-at-all</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 19:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯就“报告太过冗长”一事批评特朗普，重新提起年龄问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/harris-goads-trump-over-exhausted-report-reviving-age-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周五在竞选活动中公布了新的攻击路线，批评唐纳德·特朗普取消了计划中的媒体露面，并暗示这位 78 岁的前总统无法胜任这份工作的艰巨任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/harris-goads-trump-over-exhausted-report-reviving-age-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 19:15:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利法院反对后，梅洛尼仍拒绝移民计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/meloni-defiant-on-immigration-plan-after-italian-court-objects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼表示，在罗马法院提出反对后，她将继续推进一项有争议的计划，将寻求庇护者送往阿尔巴尼亚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/meloni-defiant-on-immigration-plan-after-italian-court-objects</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 17:49:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度被指控密谋反对的锡克教分离主义者是谁？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/sikh-separatism-explained-who-are-the-activists-india-is-accused-of-targeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官指控印度政府特工策划了一起刺杀一名美国锡克教公民的阴谋，此人寻求建立一个独立的锡克教国家。该阴谋在纽约被挫败。但大约在同一时间，这名受害者的一名同伙在英属哥伦比亚被杀，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多公开指责印度参与了此案，印度方面则予以强烈否认。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/sikh-separatism-explained-who-are-the-activists-india-is-accused-of-targeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 17:45:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古巴主发电厂发生故障，全国停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/cuba-suffers-mass-blackout-as-power-plant-fails-fuel-runs-short</link>
      <description><![CDATA[古巴岛上的主要发电厂发生故障，政府为节省燃料限制了主要产业，导致整个古巴全国断电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/cuba-suffers-mass-blackout-as-power-plant-fails-fuel-runs-short</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 17:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
